name: HarryPotterPatronusPicker

”Alexa, open Harry Potter Patronus Picker”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: harry potter patronus picker
des: Ever wondered what your patronus would be if you were a wizard in the Harry Potter world? Would it be a stag like Harry or an otter like Hermione? Just ask Harry Potter Patronus Picker and we will tell you.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
